settings.description: You have 200 seconds to pass this level
Seven short rooms, each have some puzzle element.
This is a replica of the very first Level of "Plok!" for the SNES. Also, its a test to see how well this editor was and to be honest, is kinda frustrating, but thats expected for a project in Alpha.
Chargin' Chucks lead their fellow Bob-ombs into this tight, grassy water filled course.
The sewers have been filled with water, possibly too much to handle for Mario.
